snippet.title: Jump King Ghost of the Babe Trailer
snippet.description:
When all that remains is a faint ghostly presence, what is left to jump for?

Prepare for your next challenge in "Ghost of the Babe"... Jump Kings' third map is arriving on Friday the 13th!

About Jump King:
Take up the challenge and face true high-stakes platforming in Jump King! Struggle upwards in search of the Smoking Hot Babe of legend, but explore with care; a single missed jump could lead to a long fall back down…

Jump King available now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1061090/Jump_King/

Follow us on twitter at @nexilegames → https://twitter.com/nexilegames

Find out more at playjumpking.com

Nexile is a four-man game company from Sweden, with our first commercial title Jump King we are taking our first step into the games industry.
